Apply.Name: Predicted Likely Insurance Buyers
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10036" as (SELECT PREDICTION_PROBABILITY("CLAS_SVM_1_6", 'Yes' USING *) "CLAS_SVM_1_6_PROB_Yes", PREDICTION_DETAILS("CLAS_SVM_1_6", 'Yes', 9 ABS USING *) "CLAS_SVM_1_6_PDET", "AGE", "CREDIT_BALANCE", "CUST_ID", "LAST", "N_MORTGAGES", "N_TRANS_ATM", "CHECKING_AMOUNT", "MARITAL_STATUS", "SEX", "N_TRANS_KIOSK", "STATE", "HOUSE_OWNERSHIP", "MONTHLY_CHECKS_WRITTEN", "LTV", "SALARY", "BANK_FUNDS", "BUY_INSURANCE", "T_AMOUNT_AUTOM_PAYMENTS", "MONEY_MONTLY_OVERDRAWN", "CAR_OWNERSHIP", "N_TRANS_WEB_BANK", "HAS_CHILDREN", "N_OF_DEPENDENTS", "FIRST", "LTV_BIN", "REGION", "N_TRANS_TELLER", "MORTGAGE_AMOUNT", "TIME_AS_CUSTOMER", "PROFESSION", "CREDIT_CARD_LIMITS" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

ModelDetails.Name: Model Details
ModelDetails.SQLExpression:
"N$10308.0.1" AS ( SELECT PARTITION_NAME, NODE, PARENT, LOCAL_RULE, LOCAL_SURROGATE FROM (SELECT PARTITION_NAME, NODE, PARENT, SPLIT_TYPE, DECODE(OPERATOR, 'IN', '(' || ATTRIBUTE_NAME || ' ' || LOWER(OPERATOR) || ' (' || REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE( CAST(XMLQUERY('for $e in /Element order by $e return concat(''"'', $e, ''"'')' PASSING VALUE RETURNING CONTENT) AS VARCHAR2(4000)), CHR(38) || 'quot;', '"'),CHR(38) || 'apos;', ''''),CHR(38) || 'lt;', '<'),CHR(38) || 'gt;', '>'),CHR(38) || 'amp;', '&') || ' ))' , '(' || ATTRIBUTE_NAME || ' ' || OPERATOR || ' ' || CAST(XMLQUERY('/Element[1]/text()' PASSING VALUE RETURNING CONTENT) AS VARCHAR2(4000)) || ')' ) RULE FROM DMUSER.DM$VPCLAS_DT_1_6) PIVOT(MIN(RULE) FOR SPLIT_TYPE IN ('Main' AS LOCAL_RULE, 'Surrogate' AS LOCAL_SURROGATE))),
"N$10308.0.2"(PARTITION_NAME, NODE, PARENT, LOCAL_RULE, LOCAL_SURROGATE, FULL_RULE) AS ( SELECT PARTITION_NAME, NODE, PARENT, LOCAL_RULE, LOCAL_SURROGATE, LOCAL_RULE FROM "N$10308.0.1" WHERE PARENT = 0 UNION ALL SELECT R.PARTITION_NAME, R.NODE, R.PARENT, R.LOCAL_RULE, R.LOCAL_SURROGATE, "N$10308.0.2".FULL_RULE || ' AND ' || R.LOCAL_RULE FROM "N$10308.0.1" R INNER JOIN "N$10308.0.2" ON R.PARENT = "N$10308.0.2".NODE AND NVL(R.PARTITION_NAME, 0) = NVL("N$10308.0.2".PARTITION_NAME, 0)),
N$10308 AS (
SELECT CAST('DMUSER' AS VARCHAR2(30)) as "MODEL_SCHEMA", CAST('CLAS_DT_1_6' AS VARCHAR2(30)) as "MODEL_NAME", VI.PARTITION_NAME as "PARTITION_NAME", VO.PARENT as "PARENT_NODE_ID", VI.NODE as "NODE_ID", VO.NODE + 1 as "PROFILE_ID", VO.PREDICTED_TARGET_VALUE as "PREDICTION", VI.TARGET_SUPPORT as "PREDICTION_COUNT", VI.NODE_SUPPORT as "RECORD_COUNT", VO.PARENT_SUPPORT as "TOTAL_RECORD_COUNT", VO.IS_LEAF as "IS_LEAF_NODE", VI.TARGET_SUPPORT/VI.NODE_SUPPORT as "CONFIDENCE", VI.NODE_SUPPORT/VO.PARENT_SUPPORT as "SUPPORT", RL.LOCAL_RULE as "LOCAL_RULE", RL.LOCAL_SURROGATE as "LOCAL_SURROGATE", RL.FULL_RULE as "FULL_SIMPLE_RULE" FROM DMUSER.DM$VICLAS_DT_1_6 VI INNER JOIN (SELECT VO.PARTITION_NAME, VO.PARENT, VO.NODE, VO.PREDICTED_TARGET_VALUE, O.NODE_SUPPORT PARENT_SUPPORT, decode(P.PARENT, null, 'Y', 'N') IS_LEAF FROM DMUSER.DM$VOCLAS_DT_1_6 VO INNER JOIN (SELECT PARTITION_NAME, NODE_SUPPORT FROM DMUSER.DM$VOCLAS_DT_1_6 WHERE NODE = 0) O ON NVL(VO.PARTITION_NAME, 0) = NVL(O.PARTITION_NAME, 0) LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT PARENT, PARTITION_NAME FROM DMUSER.DM$VOCLAS_DT_1_6) P ON VO.NODE = P.PARENT and NVL(VO.PARTITION_NAME, 0) = NVL(P.PARTITION_NAME, 0)) VO ON VI.NODE = VO.NODE and NVL(VI.PARTITION_NAME, 0) = NVL(VO.PARTITION_NAME, 0) and VI.TARGET_VALUE = VO.PREDICTED_TARGET_VALUE LEFT JOIN "N$10308.0.2" RL ON VI.NODE = RL.NODE AND NVL(VI.PARTITION_NAME, 0) = NVL(RL.PARTITION_NAME, 0) WHERE IS_LEAF = 'Y' ORDER BY MODEL_NAME, PARTITION_NAME, NODE_ID )
